{"tid":260461,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本韓國以為嘅滑雪地","createTime":"2017-05-27T16:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T17:39:12.000Z","uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c75e20f930b737157932156c09b0110a176acd8b","tid":260461,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T16:55:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n上年喺韓國學咗幾日滑雪 嚟緊冬天想去其他地方滑雪 順便觀光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n學生冇乜錢 計劃去啲比較平嘅地方 波蘭、俄羅斯之類<br />\nseach完一輪都冇乜收穫<br />\n俄羅斯滑雪場冇乜人講 波蘭bialka <a href=\"http://tatrzanska附近酒店hotal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftatrzanska%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97hotal.com&d=f6RU%2Fi3UOxin82MxGlYwT7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7186bde8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">tatrzanska附近酒店hotal.com</a>嗰啲好似都full晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵滑雪教練又無從入手 巴打有冇好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ea2e2ff2e53d7d3bbd5ce1a10d5f95fc3d1dc1","tid":260461,"uid":40,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"日本韓國以外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97e6b8aa0589dfb0ff490c1d24142cca1a76e8","tid":260461,"uid":93937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:36:09.000Z","msg":"加拿大？"},{"pid":"ad7b59cc4c83b074c0d1584ce2576e0b00408a68","tid":260461,"uid":92308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T17:39:12.000Z","msg":"Facebook search：Swallow Hamlet and friends<br />\n應該有人會幫到你"}]}